<task id="task_tx1_lvd_lp">
    <title>Deleting entities from the toolbar</title>
    <shortdesc>The CWRC-Writer templates come with pre existing entities as example to new users.
        You can easily delete these entities or any entities that you don't want in your document
        from the toolbar.</shortdesc>
    <prolog product="CWRC-Writer">
        <author>Megan Sellmer</author>
        <copyright>
